%% Diagram: Multi-CDN failover routing
%% Type: flowchart
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
flowchart TB
    DNS[Client DNS resolver] --> HM{Health monitor<br/>RUM + synthetic}
    HM -->|primary healthy| CDN_A[CDN A<br/>preferred]
    HM -->|primary degraded| CDN_B[CDN B<br/>secondary]
    HM -->|both degraded| ORIGIN[Direct origin<br/>last-resort]
    CDN_A --> SHIELD[Origin shield]
    CDN_B --> SHIELD
    ORIGIN --> ORIGINSTORE[(Origin store)]
    SHIELD --> ORIGINSTORE
